# S10-T04: Mascot Favicon

## Objective
Replace the generic purple favicon with Melody the mascot (idle face) for browser tab,
apple-touch-icon, and PWA manifest icons.

## Acceptance Criteria
- `public/favicon.svg` — simplified mascot head (teal body `#0E92BA` / orange accent `#FF9800`), readable at 32×32.
- PNG exports: `icon-192.png`, `icon-512.png` (and optional 16/48) generated from same artwork.
- `index.html` links favicon + apple-touch-icon to mascot assets.
- `vite.config.ts` PWA manifest icons point to mascot PNGs.
- S01 brand colours only; no new palette tokens.

## Steps
1. Author static SVG favicon from `MascotSVG` idle geometry (simplified paths, no GSAP refs).
2. Export PNGs (script or manual) into `public/`.
3. Update `index.html` icon links; remove stale `/icon-192.png` references if filenames change.
4. Update VitePWA manifest `icons` array + `includeAssets`.
5. Hard-refresh + Add to Home Screen preview — mascot visible on tab and icon.
6. `git commit -m "feat(brand): mascot favicon and PWA icons"`.
